These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, water, milk
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | 7up | milk | iced-tea | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up | soy-milk | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey, basketball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Sport   | sailing | cricket | basketball | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, dubstep, soul, funk
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
2. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
3. the fan of funk is between the fan of house and the fan of soul##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | house | funk | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, country, indie, folk
1. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | folk | techno | indie | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, video-games, collecting, baking
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | collecting | puzzles | baking | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, green, turquise, purple
