.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-11::.
City: san-francisco, rome, venice, liverpool
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to rome is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to liverpool##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| City   | liverpool | san-francisco | venice | rome |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, montecristo, pall-mall, davidoff
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | montecristo | davidoff | bolivar |

