.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
City: liverpool, edinburgh, marseilles, venice
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| City   | marseilles | venice | edinburgh | liverpool |

