.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, tulip, aconite, amaryllis
1. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | amaryllis | aconite | tulip |

 